Rename DaemonSetStatus and LoadBalancerStatus

operator-sdk can not differentiate between local and global struct
names. So it gets confused between globally defined
`appsv1.DaemonSetStatus` and locally defined `DaemonSetStatus`. Same is
the case for `LoadBalancerStatus`. Hence rename local declarations.

Signed-off-by: Janki Chhatbar <jchhatba@redhat.com>

Use the nettest image for the pause container

...used for uninstall. The K8s pause image isn’t available for all
the architectures we support or has a different name so use the
nettest image with the 'sleep' command instead.

Signed-off-by: Tom Pantelis <tompantelis@gmail.com>
